reviewText: Excellent serial from Republic studios and had the added  feature of having Clayton Moore as its co-star. Its very fast paced and action galore -highly recommend !

Another great  Republic serial, There was action  galore -and Clayton Moore dis-playing all the traits that would serve him well in just a few more months as The Lone Ranger for  the next four decades. Not much of it has really anything to do with Jesse James- its really all about Clayton for me.
Again. Loved Clayton Moore in all westerns that he stared in or even casted in. Truly enjoyed the movie. Again
